# MoreHarvest Brand Design System - Cursor Rules

## CRITICAL RESTRICTIONS
- **NEVER use CSS gradients** - Use solid colors only
- **NEVER use localStorage or sessionStorage** - Use React state only
- **ALWAYS left-align content** - No center or right alignment
- **8px base unit** - All spacing must be multiples of 8px

