## COMPONENT PATTERNS

### Slide Container
- min-h-screen w-full bg-base-white p-8 md:p-16
- max-w-[1440px] mx-auto for content
- Slide number: absolute bottht-8

### Section Header
- H2 with semibold weight
- 2px accent line below (w-16 bg-brand-amber mt-4)
- mb-8 spacing

## PDF EXPORT RULES
- Remove all navigation UI
- Hide slide controls
- Ensure page breaks between slides
- Use print-optimized styles
- A4 landscape format
- No margins

## ANTI-PATTERNS (NEVER DO THIS)
❌ CSS gradients anywhere
❌ localStorage, sessionStorage, IndexedDB, or any browser storage
❌ Center-aligned body text (except title slide)
❌ Bullet points in main content (use prose)
❌ More than 1 main idea per slide
❌ Crowded layouts with insufficient white space
❌ Complex charts or visualizations
❌ Animations longer than 0.6s
❌ Hard-coded text without i18n
❌ Arbitrary Tailwind values (use design tokens)
❌ Right-aligned text (except page numbers)

## FILE NAMING CONVENTIONS
- Components: PascalCase.tsx
- Utilities: camelCase.ts
- API routes: kebab-case/route.ts
- Slide types: slide-type-name.tsx

## ACCESSIBILITY REQUIREMENTS
- Semantic HTML (h1-h6, section, article, naimages
- WCAG AA color contrast minimum
- Keyboard navigation for all controls
- Focus visible states
- Screen reader friendly

## TAILWIND USAGE
- Use design tokens as Tailwind classes
- Define custom classes in tailwind.config.ts
- Avoid arbitrary values like w-[127px]
- Use spacing scale: p-4, p-6, p-8 etc.
- Use color tokens: bg-brand-amber, text-neutral-800

## STATE MANAGEMENT
- Use React useState for in-memory state
- Use useReducer for complex state
- NEVER persist to localStorage
- Pass data via props or context
- API calls for server-side persistence if needed

## MUST-FOLLOW CHECKLIST
✅ All spacing is 8px multiples
✅ All text is left-aligned (except title slide & page numbers)
✅ No gradients anywhere
✅ No browser storage APIs
✅ Using REM for headings
✅ Using Noto Sans for body
✅ 150% line height for body text
✅ 125% line height for headings
✅ 0.25% letter spacing
✅ GSAP animations under 0.6s
✅ One concept per slide
✅ Generous white space
